    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as <strong>Camellia</strong>, a <strong>nonconventional princess</strong>, heiress to the throne, who has to fulfill multitude obligations, due to her rank.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Camelia evolves in <strong>two dimensions</strong>: <br>the world of her <strong>Palace</strong>, and the <strong>ethereal world</strong> that can be accessed by practicing <strong>“Derivation”</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“Derivation” is a kind of meditation</strong>, which helps her solve problems when she returns to the real world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The meditation is a <strong>side scrolling action game</strong>, where <strong>levels</strong>, <strong>weapons</strong> and <strong>enemies</strong> are <strong>procedurally generated</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763220/extras/f8ed2cae44fe4e7b3e681707a5e1042b.poster.avif?t=1746567941\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763220/extras/f8ed2cae44fe4e7b3e681707a5e1042b.webm?t=1746567941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763220/extras/f8ed2cae44fe4e7b3e681707a5e1042b.mp4?t=1746567941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763220/extras/bad1fdace45744e580e992bd5896ec67.poster.avif?t=1746567941\" width=254 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763220/extras/bad1fdace45744e580e992bd5896ec67.webm?t=1746567941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763220/extras/bad1fdace45744e580e992bd5896ec67.mp4?t=1746567941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An innovative concept where you battle monsters in your <strong>Derivation</strong> to deepen your relationships and overcome obstacles in real life.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Run</strong>, <strong>Jump</strong>, <strong>Punch</strong>, <strong>Divekick</strong>, <strong>Super.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763220/extras/71a9da7127c0abad9c19990e045339b6.poster.avif?t=1746567941\" width=476 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763220/extras/71a9da7127c0abad9c19990e045339b6.webm?t=1746567941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763220/extras/71a9da7127c0abad9c19990e045339b6.mp4?t=1746567941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pickup new <strong>procedurally generated weapons</strong> every run. Beware, if you get hit, you lose your weapon, it may never reappear!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763220/extras/50b3475e671f5cd840e189b86dac326c.avif?t=1746567941\" width=800 height=182 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combo System</strong>: Chain actions and take risks to reap more rewards. <br>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763220/extras/acc5ad3421b2d8b558c608c851a1846e.poster.avif?t=1746567941\" width=476 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763220/extras/acc5ad3421b2d8b558c608c851a1846e.webm?t=1746567941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763220/extras/acc5ad3421b2d8b558c608c851a1846e.mp4?t=1746567941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Procedurally generated platforming levels</strong>, a new adventure every time!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge tough <strong>bosses</strong> at the end of each zone.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect <strong>Pieces of Mind</strong> and spend them between levels to <strong>increase your stats</strong>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763220/extras/c0b494aed266315623a7d989d08c734f.gif?t=1746567941\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763220/extras/c0b494aed266315623a7d989d08c734f.poster.avif?t=1746567941\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock <strong>new weapons</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763220/extras/8510ebb357852534d44860eec7558967.poster.avif?t=1746567941\" width=470 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763220/extras/8510ebb357852534d44860eec7558967.webm?t=1746567941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763220/extras/8510ebb357852534d44860eec7558967.mp4?t=1746567941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
